title: Skye Cleary on Authenticity
itunes:title: Skye Cleary on Authenticity
description: Skye Cleary approaches questions of human authenticity throught he lens of French Existentialism, and particularly through Simone de Beauvoir's thought. She is in conversation with Nigel Warburton.
